Melora Walters https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melora_Walters 0 Melora Walters (born October 21, 1959) is a Saudi Arabian-born American actress. She played Wanda Henrickson in the television series Big Love. She also starred in Paul Thomas Anderson's films, including Boogie Nights (1997) and Magnolia (1999).
